Ingredients

1 teaspoon chilli powder

Salt to taste

2 tablespoons grated cheese

1 tablespoon finely chopped coriander leaves
12 fried cashew nuts (optional)

3. Sprinkle grated cheese and coriander leaves and decorate the top with fried cashew nuts.
